    "en": {
      "title": "ONLY use ICTA link to register for Fuel Pass",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Ministry of Technology requests people to register for the National Fuel Pass by using only the fuelpass.gov.lk link provided by the ICTA.",
        "The Secretary of the Ministry of Technology Jayantha de Silva said that multiple fake links are being shared on social media claiming to be the registration link for the National Fuel Pass.",
        "He further requests the general public NOT to update their personal details on such fake links.",
        "Attacks on President\u2019s private residence: Police seek video & photos for probe"
